There are 7 different nationalities: american, egyptian, french, indian, italian, mexican, turkish
 1. the italian is on the far left##1
 2. the chaman-smoker is the person eating cranberry##1
 3. the french is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 4. the havana-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the american is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating apricot is in the middle##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 9. the mexican is the fonseca-smoker##1
10. the american is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the cain-smoker is the turkish##1
12. the person eating banana is the italian##1
13. the indian is on the far right##1
14. the game-smoker is between the cain-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##2
15. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
