 4. the person eating radish is between the person eating cherry and the person eating grapes##2
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person eating nectarine is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the person eating cherry is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
14. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
15. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

