 9. the teacher is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating peas##2
10. the person who's birthday is in november is the person eating eggplant##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
12. the dancer is the person who's birthday is in may##1
13. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
14. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

