7 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, mah-jongg, go, domino, bridge, monopoly
 1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person playing domino##2
10. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person playing domino##1
11. the person watching crime movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
13. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
14. the person playing domino is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
15. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching romance movies##1

