House: ranch-style, art-deco, tower, wooden, gothic-revival, modern, craftsman
 1. the firefighter is on the left of the videographer##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 3. the tower house is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the photographer is the craftsman house##1
 6. the videographer is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the wooden house is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the tower house##1
11. the person watching action movies is on the left of the bartender##1
12. the ranch-style house is between the dancer and the modern house##2
13. the tower house is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
14. the person watching action movies is the modern house##1
15. the accountant is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
