.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, cola, fanta, iced-tea, sprite
The people have 7 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking, gardening, photography, skydiving, traveling, writing
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea, marigold, rose, zinnia, daffodil, begonia
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 8. the person who growsrose is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who growsmarigold##2
 9. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
13. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who's hobby is writing##2
15. the person who growsbegonia is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
